    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Authentication landscape &amp; pattern analysis</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-8 max-w-2xl">Computed live from the verified dataset with pandas — see <code class="font-mono text-xs bg-surface2 px-1 rounded">pipeline/pattern_analysis.py</code>. Every chart below answers exactly one question.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 mb-5">
      <div class="card p-5">
        <canvas id="authChart" height="200"></canvas>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-line">So what: <span class="text-ink">{{ insights.oauth_vs_key_pct.oauth_pct }}% of apps need an OAuth2 app-registration flow</span> before Composio can call them — the single biggest driver of onboarding time across the dataset.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-5">
        <canvas id="mcpChart" height="200"></canvas>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-line">So what: <span class="text-ink">{{ insights.mcp_none_pct }}% of apps have zero MCP coverage</span> — official or community — which is the addressable surface for new Composio-built or community toolkits.</p>
